  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69eb3cf52aabb50606d62e3f",
      "text": "発話旋律",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777024253,
      "updated": 1777024253
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb3cfd00000000009b8dc3",
      "text": "[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%82%B9%E3%83%94%E3%83%BC%E3%83%81%E3%83%BB%E3%83%A1%E3%83%AD%E3%83%87%E3%82%A3 スピーチ・メロディ - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777024253,
      "updated": 1777024254
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb40bd00000000009b8df3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777025214,
      "updated": 1777025214
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb40bd00000000009b8df4",
      "text": " [スピーチ]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777025214,
      "updated": 1777025232
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb40ce00000000009b8df5",
      "text": " [発話]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777025231,
      "updated": 1777025231
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb40a000000000009b8def",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777025185,
      "updated": 1777025185
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb40b600000000009b8df1",
      "text": "> スピーチ（人の話し声）の録音から、その音程を聴き取って、音符、メロディとして、楽譜に書き取った。それを元のスピーチの録音と重ね合わせて作曲した。この手法をスティーブ・ライヒは「スピーチ・メロディ（Speech Melody）」と名付た",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777025206,
      "updated": 1777026059
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb434c00000000007d1e68",
      "text": "\t[撤回.icon]多分音高じゃないかな[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777025868,
      "updated": 1777026051
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb441800000000007d1e6d",
      "text": "\t\t\t[音程という文字列を見ると取り敢えず音高ではないかとツッコミたくなる]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777026072,
      "updated": 1777026094
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb439800000000007d1e69",
      "text": "\t\t絶対音感→音高",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777025944,
      "updated": 1777025985
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb43c100000000007d1e6a",
      "text": "\t\t相対音感→音程",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777025985,
      "updated": 1777025991
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb43d800000000007d1e6c",
      "text": "\t\tんー、やっぱり音程でも成立する。撤回。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777026008,
      "updated": 1777026602
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb40b600000000009b8df2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777025206,
      "updated": 1777025206
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb40a000000000009b8df0",
      "text": "[レオシュ・ヤナーチェク]が考案",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777025185,
      "updated": 1777025249
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb3cfd00000000009b8dc4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1777024254,
      "updated": 1777024254
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb3d0700000000009b8dc5",
      "text": "[speech melody]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
